Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.76,0:00:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(1945年2月3日)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.39,0:00:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1945年頭幾個星期\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By the first few weeks of 1945,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.90,0:00:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們從四面八方包圍了第三帝國\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we were closing in on the Third Reich from all sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.19,0:00:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在西線 盟軍突襲德國\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the west, the Allies were storming into Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.73,0:00:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(柏林上空)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.11,0:00:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在東線 蘇聯人正在接近奧得河\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the east, the Russians were approaching the Oder River.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天上 第8航空隊暢飛無阻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And in the sky, the Eighth Air Force flew uncontested.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.62,0:00:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是真正的空中霸主\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We were the true masters of the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.33,0:00:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指揮飛行員呼叫機尾 我們即將抵達目標地點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Command pilot to tail, we're about to reach the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.96,0:00:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面情況如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How are we looking back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.84,0:00:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不錯 少校 陣型整齊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Looking good, Major. All lined up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.05,0:00:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到 我們投彈吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Roger. Let's drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.63,0:00:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛機交給你了 吉恩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's all yours, Gene.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.97,0:00:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到 少校\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Roger that, Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.52,0:01:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸彈艙門打開 一分鐘后投彈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bomb bay doors opening. One minute to drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.49,0:01:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我們被擊中了  - 右側引擎正常\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Are we hit? - Starboard engines are okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.36,0:01:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是道格啊 下來看看這個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But Doug, come down here and take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兩個油箱中彈了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A couple tanks got hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.54,0:01:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 長官 來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir. On my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.17,0:01:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校 飛機受損了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Major, we have damage here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.88,0:01:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有氧氣瓶破了 我們只剩六瓶了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More oxygen bottles are ruptured. We only have six in reserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.67,0:01:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到 注意盯著點 道格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Roger. Keep an eye on it, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.76,0:01:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有火箭彈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rockets incoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.76,0:01:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一號引擎著火了 我來關掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Engine one's on fire. Shutting her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切斷一號引擎的燃料 引擎怎么樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cutting fuel and oil to number one. How's she looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.44,0:01:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 好了 火滅了... - 好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That's it. She's out. She's out. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.11,0:01:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近目標 五秒后投彈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Approaching target. Five seconds to bomb release.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.65,0:01:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投彈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bombs away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來不錯 盧克 看來我們...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Looked good, Luke. Looks like we m--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.26,0:02:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛行員呼叫機組 受損情況如何 報告\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pilot to crew, what's our damage? Report.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉恩 盧克 報告\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gene, Luke, report.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二號 四號引擎油壓下降中 三號引擎著火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oil pressure is dropping on two and four. Engine three is on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.64,0:02:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要墜毀了...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're gonna lose her. We're gonna lose her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.32,0:02:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指揮官呼叫副指揮官 接下來交給你們了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lead command to deputy command, you boys are taking over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重復 交給你們指揮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Repeat, you boys are taking over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.57,0:02:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到 我們來領飛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Roger that. We're taking the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.28,0:02:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我來駕駛飛機 好嗎  - 收到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm gonna take the ship, okay? - Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.54,0:02:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會努力帶我們穿過蘇聯前線 這樣我們就安全了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna try to get us across the Russian lines where we'll be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 長官 你來駕駛吧 羅西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir. Your ship, Rosie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托...再堅持一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. Come on. Hold together a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正在減速 要跳傘嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're losing speed. Should we bail?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不行 我們不能在柏林墜毀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not yet. We're not going down in Berlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.65,0:03:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托...再飛一會兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, come on, come on. A little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.32,0:03:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校 左翼碎了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Major, left wing is shredded.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就快到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了 要失速了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's it. She's gonna stall.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳傘 拉響警報 去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bail. Hit the alarm and then go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們能從這里飛過那條河\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can make it across the river from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.46,0:03:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我盡量讓飛機保持水平飛行久一些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna try to keep her level as long as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.67,0:03:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 快走 有煙進來了 - 是 長官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Go. We got smoke coming in. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 快...跳... - 你拿了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Come on, come on. Go, go. - You get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉恩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gene!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(奧得河東岸 德蘇前線中間地帶)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.63,0:07:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...別開槍...我是美國人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no! No, no, I'm American.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美國人 羅斯福 斯大林 可口可樂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Amerikanski. Roosevelt. Stalin. Coca-Cola.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅斯福\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Roosevelt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(根據唐納德L.米勒的著作改編)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1}空戰群英\N第一季第九集[季終]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21}本WEB版外掛字幕由  {\c&H9B30FF&}風吹來的那片云{\c&HFFFFFF&}  雙語合并
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.75,0:10:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《第九集》
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死的 23點整 還有30分鐘 不到30分鐘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Goddamn it. 2300 hours. That's, what, 30 minutes? Less.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走啊 快點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go! Hustle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有半小時 我們必須到正門去 要行進了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We got half an hour. We need to be at the front gate. We're marching.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 去通知大家 快 - 是 長官 沒問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Go tell the guys. Go! - Yes, sir. You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都出來 走了 30分鐘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone out. Let's go. Thirty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.99,0:11:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛兵們給了我們30分鐘到正門集合\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Goons gave us 30 minutes to be at the front gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.83,0:11:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,23點整就出發 他們不肯說要走多遠 多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}2300 hours, then we march. They won't say how far or for how long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.67,0:11:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30分鐘 天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thirty minutes. Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 收拾東西 走了 穿上你們最暖和的衣服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. Pack it up. Let's go. Wear the warmest clothes you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.22,0:11:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我們要去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where do you think we're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 盟軍一定很近了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know. Allies must be close.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上最暖和的衣服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get your warmest gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只帶必要物品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only essentials.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄斷就好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.62,0:11:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶上火柴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bring matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只帶不會變質的食物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only take food that will keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德國鬼子已經把罐頭戳破了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Krauts have already punched holes in the cans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會變質的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They won't keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.72,0:12:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒掉 全部燒掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Burn everything! Everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 放手 - 那是我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Get your hands off it! - That's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.15,0:12:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我更希望蘇聯人先到這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would have preferred it if the Russians made it here first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會是在想逃跑吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not thinking of running, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會是在想逃跑吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not thinking of running, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 太冷了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not in this icebox.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿漢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ham.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漢勃恩 如果我是你 我就不會那么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hambone. I wouldn't do that if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:12:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:13:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道我們什么時候 能再次吃到這樣的食物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who knows when we're gonna get this kind of food again, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾開\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何逃跑的人都將被擊斃 請不要以身試法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anyone who tries to escape will be shot. Please do not try.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蘇聯人 他們很近了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's the Russians. They're close.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是蘇聯人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's gotta be the Russians.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我閉嘴 黑鬼 給我走 快點...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shut your mouth, Black scum! March! Faster! Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們在走了...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, we're going. We're going. We're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.68,0:13:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要這樣處理恐怖傳單和殺人犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's how you handle terror flyers and murderers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.22,0:13:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用武力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With force!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.35,0:13:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所羅門 還好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You okay, Solomon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好得很 不過是個猶太人 半夜在德國散步而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As okay as a Jew taking a midnight stroll in Germany can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:14:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(德國鄉間)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(第三戰俘營西南方32公里)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 巴基提醒你了 不要... - 別說了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Bucky warned you not to-- - Don't fucking say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.89,0:14:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 你一旦有消息就告訴我 好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, look, as soon as you have anything at all, you let me know. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:14:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了 比爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks, Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒消息 還是沒有任何人的消息 羅西和機組的都沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing. Still no news on any of 'em, Rosie or the crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.49,0:15:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what's the story?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在柏林東部的無人區墜毀了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They went down over no-man's-land east of Berlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.58,0:15:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校 長官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Major, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子 你怎么來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The hell are you doing here, son?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.58,0:15:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們五分鐘后要起飛 可設備室鎖住了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We got wheels up in five, and the equipment room's locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動起來 各位 警惕點 走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's move, people. Look alive. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你這該死的... - 嘿 克勞特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You fucking-- - Hey, Clouter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你笑什么  你上周吃了一只又肥又大的鷦鷯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you laughing at? You had a big, fat wren last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜你從來沒有不帶降落傘 在德國上空飛過 是不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I guess you've never flown over Germany without a parachute, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 克羅斯比 你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I don't know, Crosby. Have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 從今往后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, from here on out,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.71,0:16:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,設備室需保持開放并有人值守 直至飛機起飛后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you're gonna keep that equipment hut opened and manned until wheels up
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30分鐘 少校 懂嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}plus 30 minutes. Yes, Major?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.05,0:16:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 懂了 少校 - 少校 懂嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yes. Major. - Yes, Major?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.84,0:16:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂了 少校\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 都聽見了 收拾一下 走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. You heard the man. Clean up. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(前往穆斯考之路)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(第三戰俘營西南方77公里)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Danke. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.11,0:17:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把路讓開\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get off the road!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 靠邊 - 把路讓開\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- To the side. - Get off the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.91,0:17:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 讓開 - 聽見沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Move! - You hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.16,0:17:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 讓開 快 - 讓路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Off the road. Now. - Move it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了鮮血和土壤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For blood and soil!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.35,0:17:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來 向我們英勇的戰士們致敬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stand up and show respect for our heroic fighters!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.15,0:17:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希特勒萬歲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Heil Hitler.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.08,0:18:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兒童和老人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Children and old men.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.25,0:18:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都完了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All is lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.69,0:18:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(穆斯考磚廠)\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}MUSKAU BRICKWORKS
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.69,0:18:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(德國 穆斯考 強迫勞動磚廠)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要跑...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't run, don't run, don't run.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 有足夠的空間給每個人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, there's enough room for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,0:18:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 靠近點...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. Get in close. Get in close.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謠言說我們天一亮就要去一個火車站\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Scuttlebutt is we're heading to a train station at first light.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謠言知道我們要去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Scuttlebutt know where we're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不確定 在黎明時分做好準備吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Just to be ready at dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.95,0:19:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況不妙 他們要把我們 送到某地去處決 不是嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This isn't good. They're gonna take us somewhere and kill us, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什么轉移我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why move us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們要真想殺我們 之前有的是機會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They've had plenty of chances if they really wanted to kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.75,0:19:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 不知道 他們是納粹 - 沒事的 所羅門\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I don't know. They're Nazis. - It'll be okay, Solly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.80,0:19:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情跟我們想象中不太一樣吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hasn't gone exactly how we thought, has it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太一樣 你希望當時做了不同的選擇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not exactly. You wish you'd done it differently?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.44,0:20:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能這么說 你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can't say I would have. You?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.41,0:20:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前也沒打算被擊落\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wasn't planning on getting shot down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我真的相信如果只剩兩架B17\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, I really did believe that if there was only two B-17s left,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那飛行員會是你和我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}be you and me flying 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.84,0:20:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有你 過去幾年會艱難得多 約翰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Last few years would have been a lot rougher without you, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Same.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.52,0:20:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們開始減速了 不是嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're slowing down, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.19,0:20:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我們在哪嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any idea where we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(紐倫堡火車總站)\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}NUREMBERG CENTRAL STATION
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.12,0:20:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紐倫堡 該死 是紐倫堡 該死的紐倫堡 我說...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nuremberg. Shit! It's Nuremberg. It's fucking Nuremberg. I me--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.08,0:20:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 冷靜點 所羅門 - 冷靜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Settle down, Solly. - Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我死定了 - 沒事的 所羅門\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm a dead man. - It's all right, Solly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在位于敵人祖國的核心 兄弟們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're in the heart of their fatherland now, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.50,0:21:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(德國 紐倫堡 第13戰俘營)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.11,0:22:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓋爾 蓋爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gale? Gale!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.28,0:22:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓋爾克萊文\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gale Cleven.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.53,0:22:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 不會吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jesus, I'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.15,0:22:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬治 你怎么樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}George. How the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.87,0:22:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離家很遠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Long way from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.03,0:22:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 嘿 這是喬治尼斯漢姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my God. Hey, this is George Neithammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.74,0:22:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 約翰 - 他是我認識的人當中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- John. - Only guy I've ever met
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.83,0:22:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 唯一一個比你還懂棒球的 - 是嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- knows more about baseball than you do. - Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.96,0:22:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你支持哪支球隊  - 洋基隊 你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Who's your team? - Yankees. You?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.17,0:22:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 小熊隊 - 總是可以明年再戰嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Cubs. - There's always next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.00,0:22:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看能不能給你們兄弟幾個 找點帳篷 生個火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So I'll see if we can find you boys some tents with some fires going.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.55,0:22:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先提個醒 通常生不了火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm warning you, most of them don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.84,0:22:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關系 能避開雪就不錯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's okay. Happy enough to just get out of the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.85,0:22:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(波蘭 前往波茲南之路)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.69,0:22:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍說他能帶你去機場\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The general says that he can take at airport
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.57,0:22:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在巴拉諾維奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}at Baranavichy,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.78,0:22:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭飛機去莫斯科\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for a flight to Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.62,0:22:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再轉機去英國\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From there to England.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.87,0:22:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他警告你 這條路會危險重重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He warns you that the road is going to be very dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.50,0:23:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會途經德黑蘭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Possibly via Tehran.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.68,0:23:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是用來擋氣味的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For the smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.23,0:23:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面有輛車掉了一個輪子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is a wagon ahead that had lost its wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.98,0:23:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們必須修好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They have to fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.36,0:23:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以走走嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you mind if I-- if I stretch my legs?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.85,0:23:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(扎比科沃)
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.83,0:26:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“生命的法官將為生命做出判決”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"THE JUDGE OF LIFE, WILL JUDGE FOR LIFE."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.44,0:26:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們找到了很多這樣的集中營\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We found many of these camps.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.40,0:26:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們到達之前 所有人都已經死了 被燒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone's already dead and burned before we arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.11,0:26:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有...更多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's-- There's more of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.70,0:27:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我們的同志甚至找到過 比這更大的集中營\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. Our comrades found even bigger camps than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.49,0:27:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們就是為了同時殺死很多人而建的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They were built for killing people, many people at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.50,0:27:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波蘭人 蘇聯人 主要是猶太人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Poles, Russians. Mostly Jews.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.09,0:27:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那輛車挪開了 我們可以繼續上路了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The wagon, it is clear. We can resume.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.48,0:27:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(波蘭 波茲南郊外蘇聯空軍基地)
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.52,0:27:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別走 少校 我去查查 下一班去莫斯科的飛機何時起飛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stay here, Major, and I will find out when the next plane for Moscow leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.11,0:27:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 尉官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.45,0:27:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪 是回家嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are you headed? Are you-- you headed home?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.00,0:27:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家 家人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Home? Family?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.39,0:28:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說他的家人都死了 埋在了他的村子里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He says his family are all dead, buried in his village.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.11,0:28:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說是他親手埋葬的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said he buried them himself
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.03,0:28:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他被德國人殺害的村民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with the other villagers the Germans killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.33,0:28:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德國人命令他把壕溝填滿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Germans, they ordered him to fill in the ditch.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.58,0:28:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面有他的妻子 女兒 孫輩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Somewhere in there, his wife, his daughter, his grandchildren.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.26,0:28:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他拿起鏟子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, he takes the shovel.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.69,0:28:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想活命 一個人必須做出選擇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To live... one must make choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.49,0:29:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在會去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where will he go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.92,0:29:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校 去莫斯科的飛機正在登機\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Major, the plane to Moscow is boarding.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.38,0:29:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與上帝同行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go with God.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.39,0:29:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說如果上帝存在 一定已經把他忘了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He says if God exists, He has forgotten him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.07,0:29:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連埋葬我們尸骨的大地都不會記得我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not even the earth that covers our bones will remember us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.49,0:29:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校...我們得走了 快來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Major! Major, we must go. Come, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.83,0:29:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.31,0:30:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(德國 紐倫堡 第13戰俘營)
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.31,0:30:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(1945年4月2日)
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.44,0:30:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.15,0:30:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德國人想要領先盟軍一步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Germans want to stay ahead of the Allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.24,0:30:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們擔心盟軍離得太近了 所以我們又要行進了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're worried they're getting too close again, so another march.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.91,0:30:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,19點整出發\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We leave at 1900 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.83,0:30:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要晚上行進\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Another night march?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.45,0:30:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 但我跟他們說一晚上最多走20公里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, but I told them we won't go more than 20 kilometers a night,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.29,0:30:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們同意了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and they agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.38,0:30:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把話傳下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Spread the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.55,0:30:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(德國 巴伐利亞 前往貝青之路)
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.89,0:30:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卜派說明天要帶我們跨過多瑙河\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Popeye's saying they're taking us across the Danube tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.56,0:30:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要么今晚行動 要么就作罷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We move tonight or we don't move at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.31,0:30:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 今晚  - 今晚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Tonight? - Tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.10,0:31:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就沒機會逃跑了 蓋爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We won't be able to make a run for it after that, Gale.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.94,0:31:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河太寬了 過去就回不來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The river's too damn big to get back to this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.23,0:31:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 大家已經開始分組\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen, guys are starting to break out into groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.90,0:31:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴克 如果我們組只有幾個人 我 你 喬治 阿林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Buck, if we keep it tight-- me, you, George, Aring--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.57,0:31:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走時就更不易被發現\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you know, it's a better chance to move unseen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.58,0:31:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- P51戰機 - 把煙和火炬都滅了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- P-51! - Cigarettes and torches, put 'em all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.21,0:31:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快滅掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Put those out!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.69,0:31:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格蘭尼茨 我們跟你說了 絕對不能晚上行進\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Glemnitz! We told you we had to stop marching at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.11,0:31:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們被自己人的飛機攻擊了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're being attacked by our own goddamn planes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.19,0:31:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 這不安全 都跟你說了不安全 - 巴基 冷靜點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's not safe. We told you it's not safe. - Bucky, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.99,0:31:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 這不安全 跟你說過了 - 約翰 看著我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's not goddamn safe. We told you. - John, look at me. Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.91,0:31:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著我 我參加\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look at me. I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.03,0:31:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們今晚逃跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We make a run for it tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.16,0:31:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點 免得他們一槍打死你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Calm down before they put a bullet in your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.04,0:32:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動起來 行進...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Move it! March, march, march!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.84,0:32:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鮑勃 去跟西門萊特說 20公里走完了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bob, go tell Simoleit we've done our 20 kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.51,0:32:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就在這里停下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're stopping here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.72,0:32:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 長官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.85,0:32:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克萊斯基 蒂勒 你們去找臨時扎營地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Korlesky, Tiller, I want you to scout for billets.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.10,0:32:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢棄建筑 教堂 學校 什么都行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Abandoned buildings-- Church, school. Whatever you can find.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.32,0:32:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰斐遜的地圖顯示 西北方向幾公里處應該有個森林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}According to Jefferson's map, there's a forest a few miles northwest.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.41,0:32:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們能跑那么遠 應該能很好地藏匿起來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we make it that far, we should be pretty well covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.45,0:32:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們能跑那么遠的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll make it that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.17,0:32:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說我們往那邊跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I say we head down that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.50,0:32:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁著還有機會 利用這個混亂場面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}take advantage of the confusion while we still can.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.09,0:32:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻過那堵墻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Over that wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.05,0:32:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 誰先去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. Who wants to go first?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.80,0:32:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.64,0:33:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 比爾 去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, Bill. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.61,0:33:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.61,0:33:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 走吧 我隨后就來 - 好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Get going. I'm right behind you. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.45,0:33:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Halt! Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.24,0:33:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 別開槍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, don't shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.21,0:33:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 快 巴克 快跑 - 站住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Go, Buck. Get out of here. - Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.85,0:33:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放了那個人 立刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Release that man. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.43,0:33:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.64,0:33:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死的 你們敢動他一根汗毛 戰俘們就會暴動\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Goddamn it. You touch one hair on his head, and you'll have a riot.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.23,0:33:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格蘭尼茨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Glemnitz.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.57,0:33:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的高級軍官之一 他是至關重要的...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is one of my senior officers, and he is essential to--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.78,0:33:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中士 命令你的人放了伊根少校\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sergeant, order your man to release Major Egan.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.78,0:33:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.14,0:34:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The hell was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.02,0:34:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬治 比爾和巴克翻過了那堵墻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}George, Bill and Buck, they went over that wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.08,0:34:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽見了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.04,0:34:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽起來像通用的車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sounds like GMCs.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.50,0:35:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來他們在撤退\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Looks like they're retreating.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.67,0:37:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死豬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.22,0:37:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.77,0:37:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.65,0:37:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.52,0:37:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.16,0:37:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fucking kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.76,0:37:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得走了 巴克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We gotta go, Buck.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.98,0:37:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Buck.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.74,0:38:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們連子彈都沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They didn't even have any goddamn bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.08,0:38:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.55,0:38:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他來了 他還活著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There he is. He made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.97,0:38:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來 少校\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome back, Major!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.26,0:38:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.18,0:38:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 兄弟們 怎么樣  - 你活著回來了 羅西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- How's it going, boys? - You made it back, Rosie!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.14,0:38:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他回來了 羅森塔爾少校活下來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's back. Major Rosenthal made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.39,0:38:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.39,0:38:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 兄弟們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.06,0:38:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 阿吉 朋友 你好嗎  - 你回來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Aggie, how are you, my friend? - You made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.31,0:38:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 嘿 別被車撞了 - 要我停車嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey, don't get run over. - You want me to stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.32,0:38:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.32,0:38:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來 羅西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome back, Rosie!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.99,0:38:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶 羅西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, Rosie!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.78,0:38:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅西 好耶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rosie! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.45,0:38:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我們從波爾塔瓦 搭乘一架C46飛往了伊朗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then from Poltava, we flew in a C-46 to Iran,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.92,0:38:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and then,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.67,0:39:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘同一架C46去了一個叫亞丁的地方 是英國基地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}same C-46 to a place called El-Aden-- which is a Brit base--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.51,0:39:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后去了雅典 羅馬 那不勒斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and then up through Athens and then Rome and Naples.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.30,0:39:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后聽好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then, get this,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.39,0:39:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們轉乘溫斯頓丘吉爾的 私人B24“解放者”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we got transferred to Winston Churchill's personal converted B-24 Liberator--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.77,0:39:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒開玩笑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I kid you not--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.52,0:39:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛回了圣茅根村\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for the flight back to St. Mawgan's.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.57,0:39:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.15,0:39:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓊怎么樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How's Jean?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.57,0:39:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她懷孕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.70,0:39:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要當父親了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna be a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.58,0:39:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.38,0:39:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克羅斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Croz.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.50,0:39:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克羅斯 恭喜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Croz, congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.34,0:39:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 我真替你們倆高興\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}God, I'm so happy for you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.26,0:39:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.47,0:39:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這...是好消息 對吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's-- That's a good thing. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.60,0:39:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 是的 - 好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yes. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.44,0:40:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確定嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.15,0:40:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確定 你知道 是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. You know, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.86,0:40:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know, it's--
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.87,0:40:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們殺這么多人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, all this killing we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.12,0:40:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日復一日\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you know, day in, day out...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.09,0:40:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會對人造成影響\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}does something to a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.84,0:40:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人變得...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Makes him...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.34,0:40:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}different...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.39,0:40:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是好的影響\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not in a good way.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.85,0:40:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅西 有時我一覺醒來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, Rosie, sometimes I wake up...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.27,0:40:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至認不出鏡子里的自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't even recognize myself in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.36,0:40:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我想起大學時讀到的一句尼采名言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It reminds me of this quote I read at college, from Nietzsche.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.37,0:40:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.00,0:41:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“與怪獸搏斗的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Whoever fights monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.79,0:41:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要謹防自己變成怪獸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}should take care not to become a monster himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.05,0:41:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為當你凝視深淵時\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because if you gaze into the abyss...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.56,0:41:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深淵也在凝視著你”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the abyss gazes right back into you."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.23,0:41:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是來和怪獸戰斗的 克羅斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're here to fight the monsters, Croz.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.44,0:41:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.57,0:41:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And, yeah--
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.91,0:41:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我們被迫做了一些難以啟齒的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, that's made us do some tough things...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.16,0:41:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們不得不做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.33,0:41:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別無選擇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.92,0:41:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人能做得出來的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The things these people are capable of...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.56,0:41:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 他們活該\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, they got it coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.98,0:42:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.02,0:42:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們活該\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They got it coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.65,0:42:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(巴伐利亞鄉間 紐倫堡南方)
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.76,0:42:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.09,0:42:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 嘿 美國人 - 別開槍 我們是美國人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey! Americans! - Whoa, we're Americans!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.64,0:42:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美國人 我們是美國飛行員\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Americans! We're American airmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.85,0:42:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手別放下來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep your hands up!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.60,0:42:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里有兩個人說是自己人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We got two here. They say they're ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.52,0:42:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們看起來像戰俘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They look like POWs.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.56,0:42:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 帶他們過來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. Bring 'em in.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.02,0:42:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 手放下吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. At ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.28,0:43:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(德國 莫斯堡 第七戰俘營)
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.87,0:43:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鮑勃 找個地方給大家避避風\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bob, find a place to get 'em out of the weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.34,0:43:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 長官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.47,0:44:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜他們不會給我們登記了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I guess they're not gonna process us.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.64,0:44:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來不會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doesn't look like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.98,0:44:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.42,0:44:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(邁克號)
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.55,0:44:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們送我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks for the lift, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.63,0:44:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校 歡迎回來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Major. Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.01,0:44:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克羅斯比 你怎么還在這破地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Crosby, they still got you at this dump?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.93,0:44:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sure do.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.22,0:44:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 少校 - 羅西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Major. - Rosie.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.56,0:44:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你回來真好 長官 - 少校 歡迎回來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Good to have you back, sir! - Major, welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.68,0:44:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊蒙斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lemmons.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.81,0:44:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 先生們 - 你回來真好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Gentlemen. - Good to have you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.85,0:44:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校 你有小帆布包嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You got a musette bag, Major?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.60,0:44:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 我落在戰俘營的套房里了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I left that in the suite at the stalag.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.82,0:44:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到的就是我的全部家當\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What you see is what I've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.53,0:45:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得感謝指揮官讓漢克去巴黎接我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I gotta thank the CO for letting Hank pick me up in Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.53,0:45:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們過去幾周執行了不少次接送任務\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've been running a few shuttle missions the past couple weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.41,0:45:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.83,0:45:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荷蘭人快餓死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Dutch are starving to death,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.58,0:45:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以盟軍在向須德海西邊和西南邊 空投大量食物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so the Allies are dropping tons of food west and southwest of the Zuider Zee.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.13,0:45:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本該跟德國人簽訂高射炮休戰協議的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Supposed to be a flak truce with the Germans,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.17,0:45:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是不打高射炮或防空炮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so no flak or AA guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.38,0:45:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們到現在也沒同意 但我們不管 還是飛任務\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So far, they have refused, but, hell, we're flying anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.02,0:45:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(蓋爾W.克萊文少校 0399782)
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.45,0:45:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊根不讓我們把東西寄給你父母\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Egan wouldn't let us ship it to your folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.70,0:45:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一直說“我等他回來” 還說“我的...”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kept saying, "I expect him back,"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.66,0:45:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我的哥們只是戰斗中失蹤”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and "My buddy's just MIA."
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.80,0:46:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么少校\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, Major,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.85,0:46:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行動部希望你不介意去飛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}operations was kind of hoping you wouldn't mind flying
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.39,0:46:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才跟你說的空投任務\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on this mercy mission I was just telling you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.73,0:46:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該會有多次裝貨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Should be a milk run,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.73,0:46:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但誰知道德國人會做什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but you can't be sure what the Germans are gonna do.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.45,0:46:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能再次駕駛飛機真好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be nice to get behind the yoke again.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.46,0:46:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴基沒能和你一起逃出來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So Bucky didn't make the breakout with you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.04,0:46:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有...巴基不得不...和其他人一起留下來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. No, Bucky had to-- He had to stay behind with the men.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.59,0:46:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過他挺好的 對嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's okay though, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.09,0:46:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 他什么時候不好過\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, when do you ever know him not to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.40,0:47:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜等戰爭結束 亞歷克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm guessing when this is all over, Alex,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.86,0:47:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們可能會從馬賽或勒阿弗爾送我們回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they'll probably send us home out of Marseille or Le Havre.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.90,0:47:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得他們不會把我們從歡樂英格蘭送走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't see 'em shipping us out of Merry Old England.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.07,0:47:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.62,0:47:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅肯 那是一架P51\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Macon, that's a P-51.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.37,0:47:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美國佬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the Yanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.08,0:47:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一架P51\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a P-51.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.46,0:47:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.61,0:47:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他又繞回來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.32,0:47:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他又繞回來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.41,0:47:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趴下 快趴下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Down! Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.12,0:47:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶 厲害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.84,0:48:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們要回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, we're going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.38,0:48:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.34,0:48:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都趴下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everybody down!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.85,0:48:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑 讓開\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Move! Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.50,0:48:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟們 端掉哨塔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fellas! Take out the tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.97,0:48:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投降吧 德國佬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Buckle, Kraut!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.14,0:48:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 各位 你們有旗幟嗎 誰有旗幟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, guys, you got a flag? Who's got the flag?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.60,0:48:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有旗幟 長官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No flag, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.77,0:49:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你們這里有旗幟嗎  - 沒有 長官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You got a flag in here? - No flag, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.27,0:49:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 旗幟 一面都沒有  - 沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Flag! No flags at all, huh? - No flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.78,0:49:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 一面都沒  - 拿我們的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No flag at all? - Get our flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.94,0:49:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 嘿...有旗幟嗎  - 我有 給\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey, hey, you got a flag? - I've got it! Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.61,0:49:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Major!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.24,0:49:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.86,0:49:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扶我上去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.57,0:49:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 別開槍 - 給我一個理由\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Don't shoot. - Give me one reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.41,0:49:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理智點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stay reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.66,0:49:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.41,0:49:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.33,0:50:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺如何啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How does it feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.21,0:50:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 好耶 - 好 把那東西扯下來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah! - Yeah! Take that thing down!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.47,0:50:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊 巴基\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go, Bucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.48,0:50:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴基 加油 好耶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bucky! Come on. Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.77,0:50:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶 撕了它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah! Tear it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.90,0:50:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶 動手 撕了它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah! Do it! Tear it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.46,0:50:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好樣的 巴基\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, Bucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.24,0:51:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美利堅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}USA!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.31,0:51:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校 戰俘營和村莊歸你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Colonel, the camp and the village are yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.19,0:51:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會在30分鐘內 讓我手下人解除武裝 向你投降\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will hand over my men, disarmed, in 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.65,0:51:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.12,0:52:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉克上校 把他們帶回去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Colonel Clark, let's get 'em back.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.18,0:52:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.93,0:53:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rosie.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.10,0:53:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.48,0:53:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些口香糖 口糧巧克力棒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some gum, D-bars,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.57,0:53:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 嘿 看這個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and, hey, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.07,0:53:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾個月以來的第一批新鮮橙子 荷蘭人可能幾年沒見了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}First fresh oranges we've seen in months. Probably years for the Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.61,0:53:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.53,0:53:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 少校 - 少校\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, Major. - Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.24,0:53:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克羅斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Croz.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.08,0:53:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去給人送糧食吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go feed some people.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.25,0:53:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 長官 好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir. Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.19,0:53:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你不介意 但我通常坐左邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hope you don't mind, but I usually take the left seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.77,0:53:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是一向坐左邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, always actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.90,0:54:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要給將軍打電話投訴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll get the general on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.57,0:54:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 我逗你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I'm just kidding you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.08,0:54:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很榮幸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.17,0:54:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好進行飛前檢查了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ready preflight checks?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.33,0:54:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就準備好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never readier.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.75,0:54:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表格1A\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Form 1A?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.92,0:54:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Checked.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.01,0:54:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制桿和座椅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Controls and the seats?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.30,0:54:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.13,0:54:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ken?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.97,0:54:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這里干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The hell you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.72,0:54:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我賭100塊 你想不到更優秀的飛行工程師了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A hundred bucks says you can't think of a better flight engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.27,0:54:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Plus, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.77,0:54:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得他真的搭一次這種飛機 會非常開心的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought he'd get a kick out of actually flying in one of these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.98,0:54:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你之前從沒乘過飛機  - 沒乘過 長官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You've never flown in a plane before? - No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.90,0:54:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 從來沒  - 從沒乘過\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Wha-- Ever? - Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.45,0:54:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我1943年乘船來到這里 然后一直沒有乘飛機的理由\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I took a boat over here in '43 and then, well, I never had a reason to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.83,0:54:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟動一號\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Start one.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.36,0:55:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯尼 風景如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How's the view, Kenny?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.03,0:55:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.69,0:55:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's something, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.80,0:55:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(1945年5月1日 荷蘭)
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.76,0:55:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導航員呼叫飛行員 轉向090 完畢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Navigator to pilot, coming around to 090, over.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.93,0:55:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛行員呼叫導航員 收到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pilot to navigator, roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.11,0:56:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.19,0:56:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好準備 各位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get ready, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.53,0:56:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近法爾肯堡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Approaching Valkenburg.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.66,0:56:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你們想祈求他們不要向我們開火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Feel free to say a little prayer that they don't open fire on us,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.24,0:56:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請盡管禱告吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if you're so inclined.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.39,0:56:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來我們安全了 兄弟們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Looks like we're good, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.81,0:56:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德國人決定遵守停戰協議\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Germans decided to honor the truce.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.73,0:56:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰明的德國鬼子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Smart Krauts.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.69,0:56:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 看這個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.21,0:57:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看見他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can see 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.96,0:57:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著投就行 道格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Drop on your best guess, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.71,0:57:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到 少校\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Roger that, Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.64,0:57:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸彈艙門打開\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bomb bay doors opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.43,0:57:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投箱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Crates away.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.82,0:57:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好樣的 我們成功了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There you go. We did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.80,0:57:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 看...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, look, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.97,0:57:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“謝謝了 美國佬”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Thanks, Yanks."
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.26,0:57:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(多謝美國佬)
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.22,0:57:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.57,0:58:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴空塔臺 這里是吃貨一號 請給降落指示 完畢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Clearup Tower, this is Chowhound One requesting landing instructions. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.86,0:58:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃貨一號 你已獲準進行上空進近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chowhound One, you are clear for overhead approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.49,0:58:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,281號跑道 1900公里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Runway 281 at 1,200 indicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.49,0:58:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風向300 風速每小時22公里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Winds are 300 at 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.41,0:58:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高度表29.96 完畢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Altimeter, 29.96. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.21,0:58:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴空塔臺 請重復 完畢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Clearup Tower, please repeat. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.46,0:58:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你第一遍就聽清楚了 蓋爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You heard me the first goddamn time, Gale.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.17,0:58:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'll be damned.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.81,0:58:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧這是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.02,0:58:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想你才怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stone in my shoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.32,0:58:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.62,0:58:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重回藍天的感覺如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How's it feel being back up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.24,0:59:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好極了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Felt good.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.08,0:59:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看是誰回來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look who's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.37,0:59:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 哈里 - 約翰伊根\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Harry. - John Egan.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.37,0:59:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你好嗎  - 很好 長官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- How are ya? - Very good, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.79,0:59:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 很高興見到你 - 彼此彼此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Pleasure to see you. - You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.21,0:59:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你還在飛機里吐嗎  - 不了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Not still throwing up, are ya? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.88,0:59:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你回來真好 - 肯尼 你好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Good to have you back. - Kenny, how are ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.25,0:59:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅西 我很榮幸 見到你很高興 你好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rosie, what a pleasure. Nice to see you. How are ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.30,0:59:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在戰爭的最后幾天 我們執行了幾次空投補給任務\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We made a few of those supply drops in the last days of the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.01,0:59:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后有一天...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then, one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.35,0:59:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天凌晨2點41分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yesterday morning at 2:41 a.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.69,0:59:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在艾森豪威爾將軍的總部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}at General Eisenhower's headquarters...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.57,0:59:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭結束了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...It was over.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.69,0:59:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約德爾將軍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...General Jodl,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.32,0:59:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代表德國最高指揮官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the representative of the German High Command,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.24,0:59:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及大元帥鄧尼茨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and of Grand Admiral D?nitz,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.16,0:59:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德國國家的指定元首\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the designated head of the German State,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.46,0:59:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簽署了無條件投降書\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}signed the act of unconditional surrender
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.54,0:59:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將所有德國在歐洲的陸 海 空軍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of all German land, sea and air forces in Europe
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.72,0:59:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給同盟國遠征軍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to the Allied Expeditionary Force
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.26,1:00:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和蘇聯最高指揮管轄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and simultaneously to the Soviet High Command.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.43,1:00:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵對關系將于今晚午夜正式結束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hostilities will end officially at one minute after midnight tonight,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.06,1:00:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即5月8日 星期二\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tuesday, the 8th of May.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.61,1:00:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但本著拯救生命的原則 昨天開始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But in the interest of saving lives, the cease-fire began yesterday
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.32,1:00:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在前線和我們親愛的海峽群島宣布停火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to be sounded all along the front and our dear Channel Islands.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.82,1:01:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 對 嘿 過來 給她... - 請再來一杯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Right. Hey, come here! Get her-- - One more, please!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.25,1:01:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暢飲吧 兄弟們 我們要回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Drink up, fellas. We're heading home.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.04,1:01:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點亮天空吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Light it up!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.26,1:01:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶 我們要回家了 寶貝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah! We're going home, baby!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.30,1:01:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們贏了 各位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We did it, fellas!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.23,1:01:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.32,1:01:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封上吧 兄弟們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Close it up, boys.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.66,1:01:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.12,1:01:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始 感覺不真實\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At first, it felt unreal,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.54,1:01:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 不可想象\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}impossible, unimaginable.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.17,1:01:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后感覺不可避免\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then, inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.25,1:01:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We were going home.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.71,1:02:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的飛機在等你 少校\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your ride awaits, Major.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.17,1:02:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.63,1:02:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要見妻子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had a wife to see.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.34,1:02:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了 哥們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.43,1:02:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見兒子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A son.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.06,1:02:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展開新生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A life to start.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.35,1:02:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我回去 最好能在明頓俱樂部見到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I better see you at Minton's when I get back.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.27,1:02:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會去的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.27,1:02:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以把小家伙帶上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can bring the little guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.61,1:02:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要我把還是嬰兒的兒子 帶到爵士俱樂部去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want me to bring my infant son to a jazz club?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.82,1:02:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 聽爵士樂永不嫌早\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, it's never too early.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.37,1:02:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會是個好父親 克羅斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're gonna be a hell of a father, Croz.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.96,1:02:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這么認為\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.00,1:02:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.33,1:03:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(百證號)
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.97,1:03:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們贏了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They won!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.64,1:04:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.52,1:04:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.31,1:04:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.31,1:04:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好回家了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You ready to go home?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.60,1:04:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好見瑪姬了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You ready to see Marge?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.07,1:04:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I bet.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.03,1:04:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表格1A\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Form 1A?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.07,1:04:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Checked.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.28,1:04:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制桿和座椅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Controls and seats?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.66,1:04:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 沒問題 - 燃料輸送閥和開關\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Check. - Fuel transfer valves and switch?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.53,1:04:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關閉的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Off.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.41,1:04:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犧牲了很多優秀的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Leaving a lot of good men behind.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.00,1:04:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多勇敢的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A lot of brave men.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.76,1:04:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.26,1:04:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中冷器是冷的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Intercoolers cold.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.99,1:05:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收起起落架\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gear up.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.96,1:05:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候 世界必須面對自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On occasion, the world must confront itself,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.80,1:05:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我們是誰來回答我們是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}answer what we are with who we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.22,1:05:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was going home.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.98,1:05:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是希望有更多人能回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just wished more of us were.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.81,1:05:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會想你們的 拜拜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll miss you. Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.36,1:05:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 拜拜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bye for now! Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.31,1:06:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 好 - 好 要飛了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- All right. - All right. This is it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.60,1:06:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,70\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seventy.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.27,1:06:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,80\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Eighty.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.69,1:06:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,90\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ninety.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.66,1:06:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here we come.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.92,1:06:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收起起落架\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Landing gear up.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.84,1:06:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攀升力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Climb power.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.56,1:07:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(哈里克羅斯比)
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.36,1:07:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(于1945年以中校身份從空軍退役)
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.70,1:07:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(回到了瓊和他們的兒子史蒂夫身邊)
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.66,1:08:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(1953年 他獲得斯坦福大學 文學博士學位)
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.62,1:08:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(在艾奧瓦大學任教幾年之后)
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.45,1:08:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(他和瓊帶著四個孩子 搬到了馬薩諸塞州)
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.75,1:08:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(克羅斯比在波士頓和哈佛大學執教)
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.80,1:08:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(30余載)
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.09,1:08:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(哈里和瓊在他們的孩子 就讀的每一所學校)
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.30,1:08:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(都擔任過家長會的聯合主席)
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.63,1:08:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(哈里克羅斯比 關于他在二戰期間經歷的回憶錄)
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.39,1:08:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(于1993年出版 哈里于2010年去世 享年91歲)
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.10,1:08:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(亞歷山大杰斐遜)
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.19,1:08:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(繼續在空軍服役)
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.57,1:08:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(直到1947年12月加入空軍預備役)
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.82,1:08:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(同年 他和妻子阿黛拉搬回了底特律)
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.99,1:08:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(成為了一名科學老師)
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.78,1:08:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(在底特律公立學校系統任教超過30年)
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.46,1:08:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(杰斐遜從空軍預備役退役)
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.54,1:08:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(身份是中校)
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.21,1:08:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(他是圖斯基吉飛行員)
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.21,1:08:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(底特律分會和全國分會的創始成員)
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.51,1:08:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(亞歷山大杰斐遜于2022年6月去世)
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.34,1:09:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(享年100歲)
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.64,1:09:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(理查德梅肯)
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.11,1:09:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(從莫斯堡解放后晉升為上尉)
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.03,1:09:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(于1945年12月從空軍退役)
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.95,1:09:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(梅肯回到阿拉巴馬州伯明翰后 創立了一所飛行學校)
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.74,1:09:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(在印第安納大學獲得數學碩士學位后)
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.33,1:09:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(他回到阿拉巴馬州 在邁爾斯學院工作)
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.66,1:09:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(1955年 他和好友亞歷山大杰斐遜 一起在底特律)
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.25,1:09:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(開始了公立學校老師的職業生涯)
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.09,1:09:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(理查德梅肯和亞歷山大杰斐遜)
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.84,1:09:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(一直是好友 直到梅肯于2007年去世 享年86歲)
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.84,1:09:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(已退役上尉理查德梅肯 葬于阿靈頓國家公墓)
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.10,1:09:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(“羅西”羅伯特羅森塔爾)
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.27,1:09:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(正在太平洋戰區 接受B29轟炸機飛行訓練時)
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.02,1:09:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(日本投降 時間是1945年8月)
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.86,1:09:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(戰后)
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.94,1:09:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(羅西在紐倫堡審判中 幫助起訴了納粹戰犯)
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.99,1:10:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(他審訊了德軍最高指揮部的主要人物)
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.99,1:10:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(包括德國空軍總司令赫爾曼戈林元帥)
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.87,1:10:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(在去紐倫堡途中)
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.45,1:10:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(羅西認識了檢察官同僚菲利斯海勒)
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.37,1:10:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(兩人不到兩周后便喜結連理)
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.42,1:10:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(育有三個孩子)
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.29,1:10:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(由于他的貢獻 羅伯特羅森塔爾被授予兩枚銀星勛章)
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.71,1:10:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(兩枚飛行優異十字勛章 兩枚紫心勛章)
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.34,1:10:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(一枚英國飛行優異十字勛章 以及法國的戰功十字勛章)
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.93,1:10:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(他在戰爭期間執行52次飛行任務)
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.31,1:10:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(是100轟炸大隊中最多的一人)
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.48,1:10:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(羅西于2007年去世 享年89歲)
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.44,1:10:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(“巴克”蓋爾克萊文)
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.36,1:10:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(繼續在空軍服役 參加了韓戰和越南戰爭)
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.12,1:10:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(他以上校軍銜退役)
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.58,1:10:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(克萊文在哈佛獲得工商管理碩士學位 在喬治城大學獲得博士學位)
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.67,1:11:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(戰后回到美國后一個月內 巴克和瑪喬麗斯賓塞結婚)
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.01,1:11:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(約翰伊根是他的伴郎)
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.51,1:11:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(瑪姬于1953年意外去世)
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.64,1:11:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(當時她與蓋爾已經結婚八年了)
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.06,1:11:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(53年后 當他87歲去世時 她的照片)
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.35,1:11:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(仍擺在他的壁爐架上)
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.48,1:11:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(“巴基”約翰伊根)
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.99,1:11:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(戰后留在了空軍)
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.11,1:11:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(在回到馬尼托瓦克后的一天晚上)
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.16,1:11:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(他碰到了高中同學約瑟芬皮茨)
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.03,1:11:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(她也還穿著女子航空勤務飛行隊制服)
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.54,1:11:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(他們于幾個月后完婚)
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.12,1:11:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(伊根上校執行過 韓戰期間的飛行作戰任務)
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.25,1:11:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(他最終成為)
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.34,1:11:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(整個太平洋地區的空軍行動主管)
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.63,1:11:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(1961年 他在五角大樓工作時 因心臟病發作而去世)
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.88,1:11:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(享年45歲 約瑟芬于2006年去世)
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.47,1:11:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(他們合葬于阿靈頓國家公墓)
